data.description: Welcome to this stately brick front home nestled in the desirable Poplar Woods community! You're first greeted by a manicured front lawn, solar accent lighting & a soaring arch above the front porch & entryway. The main floor features an open 2-story foyer, laminate plank flooring throughout, a cozy LR w/gas fireplace, a DR w/chair & crown molding, a kitchen w/ample counter space & appliances all under 3 years of age & an eat-in breakfast area. A  sunroom for watching tv or reading a good book w/your coffee in the morning, a powder room & laundry room complete the downstairs. Then head up the wood tread stairs to the upper level where you will find 4 BR's or 3 plus a bonus, your choice, and a beautiful oversized primary bedroom w/fully remodeled luxury bath. The 2nd full bath, which serves the other 3 bedrooms, was also recently remodeled! The two car garage has a new door with slide down screen making it the perfect spot for a man cave or a traditional garage. Come call this home!
